Links and info

We also a have a friendly community Slack channel - go over and introduce yourself and say hi! (please join with your full name e.g. “Ed Harris”)
To received emails about our R Users Group, HARUG!, email Ed Harris -> eharris@harper-adams.ac.uk with the subject “JOIN HARUG PLEASE”. Currently HARUG! meets Wednesday 4-5pm UK time via Teams on a variety of topics.
